skins.shipDescription: Benson-class Destroyer - Bailey, Hull Number DD-492!
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm from Planet Bunny. I'm a bunny, just like my sisters! I'm super good at giving providing fire support. I've even earned awards for it, believe it or not! Hehe, I'm super strong!
skins.acquisition: I'm Bailey, a Benson-cla... Wait, no, I'm a bunny! Commander, have you seen any of my sisters?
skins.login: Are you feeling good today, Commander? Let me inject some bunny power into you!
skins.details: Giiiy... Kiiie... Uh... Bwuuuh...? It's hard to speak like a bunny...
skins.secretaryIdle1: The most delish carrot is always going to be the next one!
skins.secretaryIdle2: I've received a transmission from Planet Bunny telling me to help you with your work. No need to thank me, just leave it to me!
skins.secretaryIdle3: I'm going to become a superstar one day! The most popular in the universe!
skins.secretaryTouch: Your hands are so warm, Commander~!

skins.shipDescription: This long-awaited day has finally come. My bunnies, are you all ready? Bailey's debut shall now begin! Commander, my sisters, let's all come see Bailey's bunny magic!
skins.acquisition: This day has finally arrived~ Are you ready, Rabbits? Bailey¡¯s new debut is about to begin. Commander, sisters, come and witness Bailey¡¯s rabbit magic!
skins.details: Cutie, Lucky, I'm leaving the equipment to you two~!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Bailey will always be shining brighter in the next moment~!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Commander, Commander! Is Bailey cute? Ehehe... you can praise Bailey some more~!

skins.shipDescription: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe¡ª the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!
skins.acquisition: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe¡ª the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!
skins.login: Trick or treat! If you don't hand over the candy, Baily and the Bunnykin will play a trick on you!
skins.details: Cutie, Lucky, listen closely! Today's mission is to extract a whole bunch of candy from the commander!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Commander, your candy contribution will be distributed among the residents of Planet Bunny! Ehehe~¡î
skins.secretaryIdle2: Don't you have any carrot candy? Bailey craves carrot candy!
skins.secretaryIdle3: Bailey's a black bunny today. Don't mistake it for a regular ol' white bunny!
skins.secretaryTouch: Candy given away can never be reclaimed~!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: This strange sensation... Could it be EM waves from Planet Bunny...?
